Title: A Lighter Shade of Fel
Description:
Dear $p,

Greetings. I have taken some time and collected my thoughts after our encounter with Lord Banehollow. 

I have also sought those who have similarly survived his dark plan, and have gathered them to me in Booty Bay so that we can decide on a way forward.

We would ask that you meet us there.

Darkest regards,

Ph'el Oman
ObjectivesText: Meet with Oman in Booty Bay.
